Just a message in the log. The workbench opened nicely.

There are two issues here.

1). Message is silently logged but the description in the log file does not 
indicate to the user whether or not it is ok. Duplicate of bug 25353.

2). Why did we have an empty markers save file in the first place? Investigate 
SaveManager code for potential answers.
